Text: this is ME!! I work across from a store and all our employees know all of them and we’re pals. anyways, there’s a girl there who’s basically my exact same stats and weight and size and she’s so pretty and always looks stylish and she’s confident and my brain just has a hard time processing that we ... take up the same physical space? and are practically the same dimensions? And I think she’s SO cute and pretty? aaaa
